Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:08.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:10.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is cooler than Kamizakura-machi Ginza.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:18.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know too much about him, but there are\N lots of other dangerous people around, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:20.65,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I saw it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:21.96,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,That black bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:25.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't had a teenage girl in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:27.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks to the info we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:32.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, I noticed I was trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:04.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the reality you perceive truly the only one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:09.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The scenery you're used to never changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:14.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your matriculation, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:19.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment, unpleasant topics like the low birthrate and the\N widening gap between the rich and poor are on the lips of all Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:25.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, were those people to gaze upon everyone at this ceremony, I'm sure they'd conclude that Japan's future is a bright one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:30.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd be assured that Japan is still salvageable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:31.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would give them strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:35.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This day will be one you all will remember. However, at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:43.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really believe that an everyday\N occurrence is unfolding here right now, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ryugamine Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:52.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A shy boy who's just come to Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:56.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sonohara Anri. It's nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:03:00.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...a somewhat aloof girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kida Masaomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:12.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I may look like an adult, but I'm just as fragile and\N vulnerable on the inside as any other fifteen year-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:14.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A boy who looks to be the only happy one in the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:18.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kamichika Rio. I hope the year goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:21.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious girl;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:25.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These sorts of people are all around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, Harima...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Harima Mika here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:35.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Absent, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:39.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a banal scene anyone could swear they've seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:43.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, starting the school year off by being late, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:45.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of self-introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Make yours from where you're standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:51.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yagiri Seiji. I hope the year goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:04:00.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, thanks to unexpected developments, another heretofore unseen reality can sometimes peer in on the present one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:04.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Yagiri, you can sit down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:05.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:07.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:13.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll be coming to school for \Na while—no, I might not come ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:14.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I came to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:22.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yagiri, what in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:29.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that's very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:32.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no time to waste with the likes of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:38.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagiri, wait. I said, "wait!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:43.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People are shocked when cracks suddenly\N appear in their peaceful, everyday lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:48.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And one girl here has peered into those cracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:53.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She should have died two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:05:00.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl was just like everyone else, born into a normal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:05.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She had no problems or inconveniences in her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:14.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, when she became a middle school\N student, something arrived at her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:28.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently my father was cheating on my mother, and they show him with some other woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And there was a note, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:33.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like, "Could you forgive this kind of thing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:37.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was sent by someone who knew the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:41.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course your father did something terrible, but that person isn't much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:50.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what to do, so I decided to hide them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:57.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, seeing my parents interact seemed gross somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:00.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been tough on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Something wrong, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:05.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I endured it for a whole six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:09.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it'd be better if everything were out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:16.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to things like that, you shouldn't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:20.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are certain things I don't really want to talk about, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:21.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they confiscated our cell phones!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:30.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:30.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.22,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:37.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if my mother just hasn't said\N anything or they talked it over while I wasn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:37.21,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,That's happened to you too, right, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:45.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even my father's lame jokes or the \Noverly-sweet taste of my mother's boiled vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:52.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought, "Why don't I just try leaving this world?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:59.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,940)}That's all I've been thinking for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:04.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:07.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not be in as bad a position as you, Magenta, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:14.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was dating someone, but she ended up doing it with my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:15.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:19.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the person I can't forgive at all is my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:20.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:26.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"This kind of thing happens all the time, and we'll just lose face if you make a big deal about it."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:29.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't say anything about how she felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:35.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And...I feel like that means our family's\N image is more important than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:40.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I guess she could've been thinking about my future...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:46.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not thinking about you at all, Nakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:49.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just thinking about herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:02.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Magenta, why don't we disappear together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:08.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we both die, then maybe they'll understand how we feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:12.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And what they should truly value the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:20.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like a stupid idea now, but that's how she felt when she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:29.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was spurred on by Nakura's words and wanted to meet \Nsomeone who was thinking the same kinds of things she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:35.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she were being deceived, there was nothing for her to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.78,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm great with girls, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so she believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:45.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you "Magenta?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then are you "Nakura?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:51.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! I knew it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.48,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as she saw his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:53.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:54.88,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,She thought, "This isn't Nakura, is it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:54.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:09:01.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet she followed him because she wouldn't be able to forgive herself if she turned back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.74,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:58.75,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.13,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, even when this happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:17.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we in the clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:23.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:26.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, sorry to deceive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:28.50,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,She was overcome with such emotions as surprise, protest, and regret...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:34.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But right before she passed out, she thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:40.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"This is my fate. It's time."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:46.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm going to disappear from this world...without anyone knowing."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:04.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a place like this by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:12.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,While she was unconscious, the world was still moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:16.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't seem like that difficult of a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:20.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:27.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Without any concern for her thoughts or wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:56.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:59.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't scrape together that kind of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying I won't pay it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:06.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if something were to happen to me, I don't know if \NMr. Shiki from the Awakusu Association would keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:07.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You old fart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:15.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I'm busy; I just don't want to spend more than 2.5 minutes of my life with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and one more guy you—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:20.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:39.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I doubt I have to remind an excellent courier like yourself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:42.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do anything more than I've asked of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:45.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just mess up the other guys a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:51.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The world moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:56.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, not necessarily in the direction \Nin which the girl believed her fate to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:57.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:20.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:07.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It said, "I was told to take you to a certain place."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:12.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bike made no sound as it moved, yet sometimes whinnied like a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:16.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt decidedly unlike reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:20.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this feeling of a body pressing against her was unmistakably real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:25.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl thought about the person on the other side of that warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:30.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they thinking? What do they know? What was their life like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:33.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she look like in the eyes of this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Magenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:41.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really Nakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:47.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same Nakura who wants to just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:55.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who saved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:57.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been tough on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:08.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:13.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm the one who had you kidnapped, Miss Magenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also the one who had you saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:29.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were going to kill yourself, but somehow\N regretted being scared when you got kidnapped...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:32.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you were to resist, then you'd be contradicting your will to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:40.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you decided to accept this as your fate,\N but you're actually relieved to have been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:43.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see the expression on your face after all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:50.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, I wanted to see your expression after I\N rendered you speechless by knowing what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:54.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:56.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:16:01.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume my response will sound quite philosophical to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:06.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, to avoid that type of explanation,\N I'll just say it's because I like humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:10.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are so interesting, so intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:15.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I simply like humans, not you in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the important part.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:22.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It...was all a lie...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:25.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you finally understand your role?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:37.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of people have jumped from this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:43.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not enough to make it famous, but I hear you'll definitely die if you jump from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:45.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, look at that splotch down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:56.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you're special, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:17:00.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're not. Everyone's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:07.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one who can live their\N whole life being completely uncorrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:12.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you have at least one or two secrets, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:16.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever thought about why\N you're so good and your parents are so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:19.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:24.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd so kindly let me give away the answer, it's because\N even if you're cheating on someone or you're being cheated on,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:29.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone laughs at bad jokes and eats over-sweet boiled vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:38.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what sort of worries you have,\N everyone's just a simple splotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:39.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Splotches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:40.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All equal before God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I let go of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:55.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:05.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I could see the full and\N awkward spectrum of your emotions today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:12.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really interested in your personal problems, but how you behave when you're worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:15.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, your behavior was as boring as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:19.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's because I knew from the start that you didn't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:23.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, then. I had fun, Miss Magenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:39.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She hesitated for an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:45.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She figured that by jumping, she could somehow hurt that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:47.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, she also thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:50.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I may have just been waiting for the opportunity."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:55.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"And that man's words are that opportunity..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:02.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, unbeknownst to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:33.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:38.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:57.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you didn't have to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:06.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl thought about her mother and father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:08.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About her father, about his mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About both her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:13.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has their own private time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:20.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that wasn't as malicious, calculating,\N or colored with hatred as she had thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:25.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it really wasn't a compromise or a way to cover up weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:31.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,930)}While looking through her house, she decided to forgive her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:37.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day, she viewed the world differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:41.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are as many memories and secrets as there are people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:45.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That realization was finally palpable to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:49.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you anywhere you want to, so pay for my meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:52.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then, how about a book store?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:56.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can find a book store on any corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:21:00.07,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Even people like these two, whom you can find anywhere, probably have their secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:21:02.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go home first, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:02.53,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,They have thoughts they don't want anyone to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:08.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagiri, isn't there something—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:13.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bu-But...being absent your first day of school...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:14.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:15.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:16.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:18.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:24.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:27.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a sinful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:27.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:30.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl with the glasses is totally into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:35.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was totally feeling unsure about the \Ndangerous and risky days she'll have with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:37.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you speak in Japanese for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:45.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For him, as well as her, reality isn't necessarily what you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:46.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And so she thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:51.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Will I be able to tell this to someone someday?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:56.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"That the world isn't as terrible as you think it is."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:05.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear anything about you becoming a crusader for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:13.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd simply asked an excellent courier to do her job...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:17.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:21.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A simple information dealer such as myself isn't that evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:28.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, I don't know if you could call someone who stops a person who wants to die from killing themselves "good."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:35.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun, you excellent courier.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.13,0:24:16.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikebukuro:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:24.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He, she, you, and I all come to this town searching for\N something, seeking something, wanting to change something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:25.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Running Rampant
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.09,0:24:27.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to eat sushi? Sushi's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.27,0:24:29.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.02,0:24:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
